doc.title: Izinto eziguquguqukayo nezisebenzayo ezitholakalayo
doc.click: : Into ye-URL yesixhumanisi esichofoziwe. Ukuze uthole imininingwane, bona
doc.page: : Into ye-URL yekhasi lewebhu lamanje (imvamisa ibha yekheli), isingeniso esinemininingwane Bona
doc.isSameDomain: : Kungakhathaliseki ukuthi igama lesizinda elifanayo, {{tt}} uyebo, {{ff}} cha.
doc.isSameSubDomain: {{ss}}: Igama lesizinda elifanayo. Qaphela ukuthi nakuba amagama esizinda esithi {{yy}} kanye ne-{{ff}} kokubili {{mm}}, amagama esizinda esincane athi {{ww}} futhi {{ffss}} ngakho-ke amagama esizinda sabo ahlukile.
doc.isSameParent: : Kungakhathaliseki ukuthi iyindlela efanayo yomzali, {{tt}} uyebo, {{ff}} uthi cha.
doc.isPageSublink: : Ukuthi ikhasi lamanje liyikhasi elincane lesixhumanisi esichofoziwe, {{tt}} uyebo, {{ff}} cha.

doc.isClickSublink: : Ukuthi isixhumanisi esichofoziwe siyisixhumanisi esincane sekhasi lamanje, {{tt}} uyebo, {{ff}} cha.
doc.isClickMultilevelSublink: : Ukuthi isixhumanisi esichofoziwe siyisixhumanisi esincane esingenamkhawulo sekhasi lamanje, {{tt}} uyebo, {{ff}} cha.
